happy holidays everyone have a merry christmas with your family all of you enjoy kinship winter arrives shining dictation the wet leaves give me dressed in silence and yellow i am a book of snow a spacious hand an open meadow a circle that waits i belong to the earth and its winter earths rumor grew in the leaves soon the wheat flared up punctuated by red flowers like burns then autumn arrived to set down the wines scripture everything passed the goblet of summer was a fleeting sky the navigating cloud burned out i stood on the balcony dark with mourning like yesterday with the ivies of my childhood hoping the earth would spread its wings in my uninhabited love i knew the rose would fall and the pit of the passing peach would sleep and germinate once more and i got drunk on the air until the whole sea became the night and the red sky turned to ash now the earth lives numbing its oldest questions the skin of its silence stretched out once more i am the silent one who came out of the distance wrapped in cold rain and bells i owe to earths pure death the will to sprout pablo neruda

every picture tells a story heres the story this picture was taken after we visited longewala border while returning back to our tents in sam sand dunes we could not control ourselves to not stop for the beautiful sunset we had to cross a patch of kms till ramgarh for petrol pump which was scary as the sun was set and because it was bsf area there were no shops no petrol pumps not even a single person on the road except the four of us riding in cold desert me and my friend nitesh who had old gen dukes were low on fuel as our tank capacity is pretty low than the new duke dhruketpatel and were unknown about this situation of there being no petrol pump for about more than kms it was extremely scary as we were worried of getting out of fuel in the middle of open barren land with snakes crossing our path and all the insects coming out of the sand dunes in the night time we both riding at an economy pace to conserve fuel and waiting for the ramgarh city petrol pump those kms were like a lot at that moment but thanks to our prayers the moment we reached the fuel station nitesh bike was completely out of fuel and so we managed to reach our tents after that saurabh

gods plan every year has its ups and downs and this year was no different after the wedding and traveling we found out caryn had to undergo a second operation for endometriosis which would raise the infertility level higher as a woman gets older through her relentless hours of research and seeking answers god heard all our prayers and is blessed us with a baby weeks right after the surgery as a guy heres a few things i took away from this endometriosis is a different type of animal that most women do not know about actually even many doctors including obgyns we had to see a specialist who focuses on it rather vs a doctor that only knows about it and gives common practices thank you endometriosissurgeon we knew to trust you when you posted never ever consult a doctor with tattoos dont be afraid to seek for answers caryn joined many facebook groups and blogs to learn from other women that been through it just like in life finances fitness take advice from people that actually have what you want and been through it many people have been taking textbook advice about this subject if you know somebody going through this feel free to ask caryn she may be of great resource shes been of help to many people have faith and trust the process theres a timing for everything so you gotta be in a positive mental state of mind it may seem shitty at the moment but see the good from situation outside i was telling caryn everything will be okay while inside i had many what if thoughts stay strong we want to thank all our family and friends who comforted and prayed for us during this last half year weve been waiting to share this miracle blessing with you wishing everybody a happy holidays

fda warns against use of teething jewelry reuters babu joseph reports that in a warning the food and drug administration is now urging parents to stay away from socalled teething jewelry that is necklaces and bracelets used to relieve teething pain in infants the fdas action comes after reports of a death and several serious injuries in a statement fda commissioner scott gottlieb said consumers should consider following the american academy of pediatrics recommendations of alternative ways for treating teething pain such as rubbing inflamed gums with a clean finger or using a teething ring made of firm rubber whats more the fda said it would monitor reports of adverse events related to teething jewelry adding that it continues to recommend that caregivers avoid using teething creams benzocaine gels sprays ointments solutions and lozenges for mouth and gum pain
